 And I got to tackle all my programs, try to find holes in them.

47:22.960 --> 47:26.880
 And I rewrite the programs over after I get a better idea.

47:26.880 --> 47:29.080
 Is there ever dead ends?

47:29.080 --> 47:32.200
 Oh yeah, I throw stuff out, yeah.

47:32.200 --> 47:38.360
 One of the things that I spent a lot of time preparing, a major example based on the game

47:38.360 --> 47:40.600
 of baseball.

